My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 11

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

South Australian homemakers, mums and friends Bree and Jessica host their instant restaurant. With a love of entertaining and tourism, they hope to showcase a worldly adventure away from home.
